sequenceDiagram
    participant F as Frontend (app.js)
    participant API as ChatbotAPI (FastAPI)
    participant OA as OpenAIClient
    participant US as UserSession
    participant U as Utils
    F->>API: POST /chat (message, user_id)
    API->>U: sanitize_input(message)
    API->>US: add_message(message)
    API->>OA: generate_response(prompt)
    OA-->>API: response
    API->>US: add_message(response)
    API->>U: log_event('response sent')
    API-->>F: response
    F->>API: GET /history (user_id)
    API->>US: get_history()
    API-->>F: history
